
---------------------------------------------
|||| Service Console PLugin Installation ||||
---------------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/user/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /path/to/ServiceConsolePlugin/ServiceConsole/* /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /path/to/twister/config/plugins.xml

append config:

<Plugin>
	<name>ServiceConsole</name>
	<jarfile>ServiceConsole.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>ServiceConsole.py</pyfile>
	<status>disabled</status>
</Plugin>

